      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's full of character! This vehicle has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next adventure. While it shows some honest signs of wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for a great value. It\u2019s the perfect opportunity to own a quality car that you can continue to enjoy and improve over time!",
